					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">L-proger wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">But i want to understand, why not read it immediately? Why CPU needs that delay?  And why then reading of $3F00-$3FFF should not be delayed??</div>
<br />Most of us don't know about the hardware details, so I'm not sure you'll get a definitive answer to this. What we DO know though is that the pattern and name tables, which are affected by the delay, are memory chips separate from the PPU chip, but the palette RAM is internal to the PPU, so it doesn't have to make any external memory accesses to fetch data from it.</div>

